data.description:
Introducing a charming split-level home featuring three bedrooms, one and a half baths, and a new roof installed in 2021. This lovely property is situated on a generous corner lot and offers over 1,500 square feet of living space. The main level welcomes you with a spacious living room, a cozy dining area, and a well-equipped kitchen, filled with natural light from large windows. Upstairs, you'll discover three comfortable bedrooms and a full bathroom, perfect for families or those in need of extra space. The lower level boasts a unique half bath, laundry area, and a spacious family room, making it an ideal space for entertaining or movie nights. The fenced yard and generous corner lot provide privacy and space for outdoor activities and gardening. Plus, there's a three-season room off the dining room and garage, adding valuable extra space.

This charming split-level home offers a combination of living space, outdoor amenities, and mechanical updates. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it your own. Schedule a showing today to experience the warmth and comfort of this fantastic property.
